
                                                        +-------+
                                                        |  .SS  |
                                                        +-------+

SINGLE SPACE causes lines  output to the text area  to be single-
spaced.

     +-------+---------------------------------------------+
     |       |                                             |
     |  .SS  |                                             |
     |       |                                             |
     +-------+---------------------------------------------+

This  control word  causes  a break.    At  the  start of  SCRIPT
processing, single-spacing is in effect.  The .SS control word is
equivalent to the ".LS 0" control word.

